# Module: tf.contrib.keras



Defined in [`tensorflow/contrib/keras/__init__.py`](https://www.github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/r1.4/tensorflow/contrib/keras/__init__.py).

Implementation of the Keras API meant to be a high-level API for TensorFlow.

This module an alias for [`tf.keras`](../../tf/keras), for backwards compatibility.

Detailed documentation and user guides are also available at
[keras.io](https://keras.io).
